20
1995:28:30,933.3330001831055 --> 2098:13:30,933.3330001831055
He too will earn forgiveness."

21
2098:15:10,933.3330001831055 --> 2142:28:30,933.3330001831055
[g@Wukong smiled.

22
2142:30:10,933.3330001831055 --> 2311:40:10,933.3330001831055
"See, Master? We are all thankful."@g]

23
2311:41:50,933.3330001831055 --> 2516:00:10,933.3330001831055
They continued up the mountain and were soon surrounded by clouds.

24
2516:01:50,933.3330001831055 --> 2647:31:50,933.3330001831055
Bright light shone from the Thunderclap Monastery above.

25
2647:33:30,933.3330001831055 --> 2781:30:10,933.3330001831055
The travelers arrived at an enormous gate, where two guards stood.

26
2781:31:50,933.3330001831055 --> 2997:53:30,933.3330001831055
