"Thank you," said the Tang Monk.

68
7976:18:30,933.3330001831055 --> 8237:10:10,933.3330001831055
"What a relief!" said Bajie.

69
8237:11:50,933.3330001831055 --> 8411:51:50,933.3330001831055
